            "title": "Make less",
            "body": "Scarcity isn't a tactic - it's the only way five of us make things we're proud of."
          }
        },
        "val_2": {
          "type": "value",
          "settings": {
            "title": "By hand",
            "body": "Every piece packed in the room we work in. No third-party bullsh*t."
          }
        },
        "val_3": {
          "type": "value",
          "settings": {
            "title": "No restocks",
            "body": "When a chapter sells out, it's gone. The work stays honest because we can't lean on a warehouse of safe reprints."
          }
        },
        "val_4": {
          "type": "value",
          "settings": {
            "title": "From the East",
            "body": "Born in a Kaunas garage. The most interesting streetwear isn't where you think it is."
          }
        }
